    store64(p + PROF_SPIRIT, "Your nature is visionary metaphysics. You did not choose between reason and revelation — you wove them into a single fabric so vast it contains every contradiction without strain. Your wahdat al-wujud is not pantheism but the recognition that there is nothing but God's face, wherever you turn.");
